name: Muay Thai Clinch Room
description:
Muay Thai "Clinch Room" is clinch drill that 1 fighter clinch with 4-5 fighters.
"The One fighter" can not take a rest.When he falls or his foe fall,new fighter will come clinch him immediately. !!!Non-Stop!!! It takes at least 30 minutes up to 1 hour drill.
It is very tough clinch drill.
